Taken from Example and Test Vector for the ChaCha20 Cipher of https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc8439#section-2.4.2

To test yourself here is the key, nonce, and counter below.

uint8_t key[32] = {0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00,
                       0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00,
                       0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00,
                       0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x01};
    
uint8_t nonce[12] = {0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x00, 0x02};
    
uint32_t counter = 1;
